{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-1-chapter-level-1-tsx","path":"/topics/diarrhoea-prevention-advice-for-travellers/have-i-got-the-right-topic/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"47ddb819-f046-5e92-999c-a3d47a00ede8","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","depth":1,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 4b466fc8-8e04-401c-81a3-b115ba91137c --><h1>Have I got the right topic?</h1><!-- end field 4b466fc8-8e04-401c-81a3-b115ba91137c -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item a2fed32c-1421-4350-b94c-4206621d1f79 --><!-- begin field f8abd7cd-eb55-4795-8580-acbd00883368 --><p>From age 1 month onwards.</p><!-- end field f8abd7cd-eb55-4795-8580-acbd00883368 --><!-- begin field d9fd483f-d9f5-4482-917c-1bcfe64fac0d --><p>This CKS topic covers the prevention of travellers' diarrhoea, and includes the use of antibiotics for the prophylaxis and empirical treatment of travellers' diarrhoea.</p><p>This CKS topic does not cover the assessment of diarrhoea, the management of acute gastroenteritis (including presumed infectious gastroenteritis) in adults and children, diarrhoea due to food poisoning, or antibiotic-associated diarrhoea. These are covered in the CKS topics on <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/diarrhoea-adults-assessment/\">Diarrhoea - adult&#39;s assessment</a>, <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/diarrhoea-antibiotic-associated/\">Diarrhoea - antibiotic associated</a>, and <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/gastroenteritis/\">Gastroenteritis</a>. </p><p>There are separate CKS topics on <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/gastrointestinal-tract-lower-cancers-recognition-referral/\">Gastrointestinal tract (lower) cancers - recognition and referral</a>, <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/gastrointestinal-tract-upper-cancers-recognition-referral/\">Gastrointestinal tract (upper) cancers - recognition and referral</a>, <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/irritable-bowel-syndrome/\">Irritable bowel syndrome</a> and <a class=\"topic-reference external-reference\" href=\"/topics/palliative-care-nausea-vomiting/\">Palliative care - nausea and vomiting</a>.</p><p>The target audience for this CKS topic is healthcare professionals working within the NHS in the UK, and providing first contact or primary healthcare.</p><!-- end field d9fd483f-d9f5-4482-917c-1bcfe64fac0d --><!-- end item a2fed32c-1421-4350-b94c-4206621d1f79 -->","topic":{"id":"d5cf1db6-a6d9-54fb-b393-095d8af57067","topicId":"9042b194-f66e-44c6-a91c-76ffa626e3e8","topicName":"Diarrhoea - prevention and advice for travellers","slug":"diarrhoea-prevention-advice-for-travellers","lastRevised":"Last revised in February 2019","chapters":[{"id":"3f7bee04-88e6-5a40-86d5-e39dc29e4059","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"47ddb819-f046-5e92-999c-a3d47a00ede8","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"bdd3d81e-da2b-5807-b257-8dd4d73a596c","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"5ac4ad9d-b3fb-51c6-84de-19181b30e02c","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"5568a30c-164d-5d4f-8d41-ad7eff1173cb","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"6f04e901-40c5-5906-a7eb-5935a99758bb","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"e0f32109-cb0a-51e3-aa59-bcac4a364a5f","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"4a74f052-b6c8-5743-b69f-30ffc630174e","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"81c43095-b29a-537e-ad23-56ca74d2e6fb","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"6e2e9744-c361-5fb3-91e7-f843ad784aec","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"09edec10-2e6b-